Happy Earth Day! 🌎 Stellabrate by learning simple ways to be more sustainable around the house! 💡How about repurposing and upscaling all those Stella Rosa bottles? Watch our latest episode of Stellabration Education with Nina Chantele and the Stella Rosa team to get inspired with a few creative DIY bottle crafts! 💚

🌟 Don’t forget to enter the Green Queen Giveaway by submitting a pic of your creation for your chance to win a $500 Visa gift card and merch! 

Visit the 🔗 in our bio to enter!

node.title: Stellabration Education Episode 3: DIY Bottle Crafts

Satisfy your senses and sweet tooth with this irresistible Summer treat! 🍹😋 See the recipe 👇🏽. ⁣
⁣
🍉 WATERMELON SUGAR 🍭⁣
⁣
- 4 oz Stella Rosa Watermelon⁣
- 3/4 oz fresh lemon juice⁣
- 1 oz vodka ⁣
- Coarse pink sugar and honey (for rim)⁣
- Mint, lavender, and a strawberry slice (for garnish) ⁣
⁣
1. Rim your glass with honey and then coat evenly in pink sugar. ⁣
2. Add vodka, lemon juice, and Stella Rosa Watermelon into a cocktail shaker with ice. ⁣
3. Gently stir and strain into the rimmed glass. Garnish with mint, lavender, and a strawberry slice. enjoy!⁣
⁣

- 3/4 oz fresh lemon juice⁣
- 2 oz bourbon⁣
- 1 orange, sliced⁣
- Blackberries, dried rosebuds, and a rosemary sprig (for garnish) ⁣
⁣

node.text:
Is your Stella Rosa squad asking for new cocktails?✨🤔 Impress your guests and slush their mouths with this refreshing Frosé recipe ft. our flavor of the month, Stella Rosa Watermelon! 🍉🍨
⁣
𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬:⁣
- 1 bottle Stella Rosa Watermelon⁣
- 4 cups diced watermelon⁣
- 4 cups Stella Rosa Watermelon ice cubes. ⁣
- 1 oz vodka⁣
- 1 whole watermelon, carved and cut into a bowl. ⁣
- Mint (for garnish)
⁣
⁣
𝐈𝐍𝐒𝐓𝐑𝐔𝐂𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍𝐒: ⁣
1. Place 4 cups of diced watermelon cubes in a plastic bag and freeze overnight. ⁣
2. Pour Stella Rosa Watermelon into 2 ice cube trays and let freeze overnight. ⁣
3. Pour rest of wine into blender, along with frozen watermelon, vodka, and Stella Rosa Watermelon ice cubes. Blend until smooth. ⁣
4. Pour slushy into a bowl-shaped carved watermelon, garnish with mint, and enjoy!⁣
⁣
⁣⁣

🌶 A drink that is spicy and sweet is the ultimate treat! 🍭 Taste the magic of Tropical Mango in a frozen cocktail that’s sure to energize your taste buds. 😋 See the recipe 👇🏽. ⁣
⁣
𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬:⁣
🥭 1 cup Stella Rosa® Tropical Mango⁣
🥭 1 cup frozen mango⁣
🥭 3 oz. Vodka⁣
🥭 Ice⁣
🥭 Lime⁣
🥭 Chili powder (for rim)⁣
⁣
𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬: ⁣
1. Run a lime around the rim of your glasses and roll in chili powder.⁣
2. In a blender, combine all other ingredients and blend until fully incorporated together.⁣
3. Pour into glasses and garnish with a lime wheel. Enjoy!⁣
⁣
